caption:
New In! 🔥 | Audi Rally Quattro Group B 1984. 

A 1:8 scale beast built from 3886 pieces of pure motorsport adrenaline.
With remote-controlled 4WD, a fully functional engine, LED lights, and that legendary boxy stance, this isn’t just a model. It’s a tribute to a rally icon.

Group B never died — it just got bricked.

#buildtheunimaginable #24builds
